</fr:meta>
          </fr:frontmatter>
          <fr:mainmatter><fr:p>Let <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[H \colon  f \sim  g]]></fr:tex> be a <fr:link href="foreign-erct-erct-0014.xml" title="Homotopy" addr="//erct/erct-0014" type="local">homotopy</fr:link> between two functions <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[f,g\colon  A \to  B]]></fr:tex>. For any identification <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[p\colon  x =y]]></fr:tex> in <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[A]]></fr:tex>, we have an identification <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[H x \cdot  \mathsf {act}_{g}\,p = \mathsf {act}_{f}\,p\cdot  Hy]]></fr:tex>.</fr:p>
 
   
   <fr:tree show-metadata="false" toc="false"><fr:frontmatter><fr:authors><fr:author><fr:link href="foreign-erct-jonmsterling.xml" title="Jon Sterling" addr="//erct/jonmsterling" type="local">Jon Sterling</fr:link></fr:author></fr:authors><fr:date><fr:year>2023</fr:year><fr:month>12</fr:month><fr:day>21</fr:day></fr:date><fr:anchor>10461</fr:anchor><fr:addr type="machine">//erct/unstable/447</fr:addr><fr:route>foreign-erct-unstable-447.xml</fr:route><fr:title text="" /><fr:taxon>Proof</fr:taxon></fr:frontmatter><fr:mainmatter>
 <fr:p>By identification induction on <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[p]]></fr:tex>, it suffices to show that <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[Hx\cdot \mathsf {refl} = \mathsf {refl}\cdot  Hx]]></fr:tex>.</fr:p>
</fr:mainmatter></fr:tree>
 
